  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients having total proctocolectomy with ileal pouch anal anastomosis.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  hypoalbuminemia

          -  prolonged steroid use

          -  anemia

          -  anastomosis under tension

          -  leak with air test

          -  bleeding

          -  poor vascular supply of anastomosis
      </textblock>
